sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Button as button.submit
    participant Div as div.form-wrapper
    participant Main as main
    participant Body as body
    participant Doc as document

    User->>Button: Click
    Note over Button: Target phase — event fires on target
    Button->>Button: Run button click listeners
    Note over Button,Doc: Bubble phase — event propagates upward
    Button->>Div: Event bubbles to div.form-wrapper
    Div->>Div: Run div listeners (if any)
    Div->>Main: Event bubbles to main
    Main->>Main: Run main listeners (if any)
    Main->>Body: Event bubbles to body
    Body->>Body: Run body listeners (if any)
    Body->>Doc: Event bubbles to document
    Doc->>Doc: Run document listeners (event delegation here)
    alt stopPropagation called at any level
        Note over Button,Doc: Propagation halted — no further bubbling
    end
